According to the [[2010 United States Census|Census of 2010]],<ref name="GR2">{{cite web|url=https://www.census.gov|publisher=[[United States Census Bureau]]|accessdate=2008-01-31|title=U.S. Census website}}</ref> there were 10 people living in Tat Momoli. The [[population density]] was 4.16 people/km<sup>2</sup>. Of the 10 residents, Tat Momoli was composed of 10% [[Race (United States Census)|whites]], 60% [[Race (United States Census)|American Indians or Alaska Natives]], and 30% were [[Race (United States Census)|some other race]]. Out of the total population 30% were Hispanic or Latino of any race.<ref name="GR3-u">{{cite gnis|24644|Tat Momoli|2026-02-01}}</ref>

